1.Mathematical & Logical Blocks
Arithmetic: +, -, *, /, % (Modulus), // (Floor Division), ** (Exponentiation)
Comparison: ==, !=, >, <, >=, <=
Logical: and, or, not
Membership/Identity: in, not in, is, is not

2.Order of Precedence Hierarchy
() — Parentheses
** — Power Alignment
*, /, //, % — Multiplicative Group
+, - — Additive Group
==, !=, <, >, in, is — Comparison Checkers
not, and, or — Logical Progression